{"tid":1323533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮族遊行發出《不反對通知書》","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T17:31:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"40cf5d5a7419f9d0fe97f6cd7053015e67af4a92","tid":1323533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"銀髮族717遊行最新消息 :<br />\n<br />\n警方最終發出《不反對通知書》<br />\n<br />\n7月17日（星期三）下午5時<br />\n 遮打花園➡️政府總部<br />\n<br />\n我們要求：<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n2. 立即撤銷對已被捕人士的檢控<br />\n3. 立即停止搜捕<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會徹查警民衝突、警方濫用暴力的緣由和責任<br />\n5. 重啟政改, 實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n(請穿白衫黑褲，默默為崩壞制度送終)<br />\n<br />\n大家可以可以自帶寫上簡單心聲的示威牌，參與是次靜默遊行。<br />\n<br />\n參加者宜帶備充足食水、毛巾、替換上衣(因天氣酷熱。)"},{"pid":"e266ba572a5dc758ef9e77c5c09812a09a56c8c0","tid":1323533,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8e0b337c92b15e0c79ae88f4f294953dd2c1dd3","tid":1323533,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"有用"},{"pid":"0b058120356a0d3b6079a0c24a32494bfca916a7","tid":1323533,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"e68eb3294f493d4ddf3d731c5eb343238b195319","tid":1323533,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:31:06.000Z","msg":"有人冇警"},{"pid":"26726bbc2b876b9372b5f485c64f35a17df57757","tid":1323533,"uid":19707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fbdb015fe8f9bf81901ac0eb5f1ccae5a82f96","tid":1323533,"uid":705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"係咪又打算圍哂去路之後再打人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連銀髮族都要屈衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac07c265fea7febaf5f